          <title>Syracuse rallies to force overtime and beat No. 25 UNLV 44-41, spoiling Rebels' poll debut</title>
          <description><![CDATA[LeQuint Allen powered into the end zone from a yard out in overtime to give Syracuse a 44-41 victory over No. 25 UNLV on Friday night, four days after the Rebels broke into the AP Top 25 for the first time in program history.]]></description>
