        <item>
          <title>NFL says the preseason saw its fewest number of concussions since tracking started</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The NFL saw its fewest number of concussions in the preseason since tracking started in 2015. There were 44 concussions in practices and games, a decrease of about 24% from last year.]]></description>
